s/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e56abe71798ba5f38e15cb2314ee11f5bf1b69dc","tid":671172,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T09:07:06.000Z","msg":"福仁嘅電腦醫院？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07055c8cfead67805f57066c48b0a8189397c294","tid":671172,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T12:13:51.000Z","msg":"如果唔識揀就買隻六七百蚊火牛"},{"pid":"d89e0a95d24e04bfefb1f63fefdac51898db93e0","tid":671172,"uid":161918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T11:10:38.000Z","msg":"我以前都試過部機無啦啦斷電 reboot<br />\n<br />\n之後膽粗粗買左隻牛自己換 又真係搞店左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n反正買隻牛好平 你咪試下囉"},{"pid":"2389ab2f454967a7129b35d6d5237a1d957c4d2c","tid":671172,"uid":119169,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T11:23:50.000Z","msg":"其實好易  <br />\n1.死顯示卡就插內顯試,好易睇到<br />\n<br />\n2.1.唔著機無電就買隻2手牛試下,反正超平<br />\n2.2.換左牛都唔著就9成9底板出事,2手板又係好平<br />\n<br />\n3.RAM都幾難壞,同埋唔會無電著,好易睇得出<br />\n4.HDD壞,呢個就預左買過隻新啦,因為要整貴+煩"},{"pid":"b38637f3793c093574c3be7e90dd215e1723a0cd","tid":671172,"uid":221007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"136c018b51f3c6bbbf62289096c73c26bd4137d7","tid":671172,"uid":1048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T05:27:15.000Z","msg":"我部電腦而家打機嗰陣 通常一開始遊戲入場嗰一下 就會自己好似停咗一下電咁重開機 係咪通常都係火牛有事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T02:14:49.000Z","msg":"想問最後搞成點<br />\n<br />\n因為我依家部電腦都係咁<br />\n<br />\n自己又唔識搞<br />\n<br />\n拎左落樓下電腦鋪睇又話冇事<br />\n<br />\n想另外再搵人維修"}]}